hh3cWebAuthentication.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cWebAuthentication.description: The MIB module is used for web authentication to send traps.

hh3cWaVlanID.name: hh3cWaVlanID
hh3cWaVlanID.description: The Vlan ID associate with the port and the MAC address.

hh3cWaReasonCode.name: hh3cWaReasonCode
hh3cWaReasonCode.description: The code indicates the reason for the action of this trap. globalNumberMax: The global number of connections is up to max. configNumberMax: The global number of connections is up to configured max value. portNumberMax: The interface number of connections is up to max. invalidUsername: The username or password is too long or username is empty. authFail: Wrong username or password. setACLFail: Failed to set ACL. changeVlanFail: Failed to set VLAN. other: Other reasons. onlineOverTime: The online time is over the max value. noTransferData: There was no data flow for the connection. cutOperation: There was a cut operation. portDisabled: Web authentication was disabled on interface. portDown: The interface turned down. userLogout: The client required to logout. vlanChanged: The interface VLAN value was changed. vlanDelted: The interface VLAN was deleted.

hh3cWaActionCode.name: hh3cWaActionCode
hh3cWaActionCode.description: The code indicates the system action. enabled: Web authentication turns enabled. disabled: Web authentication turns disabled.

hh3cWaClientMacAddr.name: hh3cWaClientMacAddr
hh3cWaClientMacAddr.description: The MAC address of the client.

hh3cWaClientLogon.name: hh3cWaClientLogon
hh3cWaClientLogon.description: It is generated when a client succeeded to logon.

hh3cWaClientLogonFail.name: hh3cWaClientLogonFail
hh3cWaClientLogonFail.description: It is generated when a client failed to logon, the hh3cWaReasonCode shows the failure reason.

hh3cWaClientLogout.name: hh3cWaClientLogout
hh3cWaClientLogout.description: It is generated when a client logout, the hh3cWaReasonCode shows the logout reason.

hh3cWaSysAction.name: hh3cWaSysAction
hh3cWaSysAction.description: It is generated when a system action was occurred, the hh3cWaActionCode shows the action information.
